    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A ray of sickening greenish energy lashes out toward a creature within range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes [[/damage 2d8 type=poison]] damage and must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, it is also &amp;Reference[condition=poisoned] until the end of your next turn.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by [[/damage 1d8]] for each slot level above 1st.</p></div></div>",
